{"tid":1676492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"知己知彼百戰百勝","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T13:27:11.000Z","uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"391119ca7d362966eb1a6f689322d59722d32e6f","tid":1676492,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩參加象棋交流會<br />\n有 D 中國棋手同經常往來中國既香港棋手<br />\n佢地形容中國經濟狀態，比香港新聞報導既消息更大獲<br />\n<br />\n中國2019年玩緊一種叫「永續銀行」既經濟模式<br />\n蝕緊錢既銀行，或已經負資產既銀行，可以括免提交銀行報告，即係唔會知道間銀行狀態 (當然可以用逆思維推斷)<br />\n即係中國既銀行唔知幾時會突然仆街<br />\n<br />\n另一樣唔關經濟事，中國小學教學生玩鬥地主(唔係啤牌個 D)、打倒土豪<br />\n(佢地比相我睇，但冇 send 比我，信就信，唔信當我鳩up 都冇所謂)<br />\n個畫面同當年文化大革命 D 紀錄片同相基本上係一樣，睇黎準備玩 第二次文革"},{"pid":"5f33ffe4ce09a3ced72a770fb87df940b83265b5","tid":1676492,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:20:42.000Z","msg":"要做仔細研究同solid既proof"},{"pid":"d58046fc987c486708590b786a2cbc43b2eb0960","tid":1676492,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"86827b8179b1a81714f763d60ab6ec41165d5259","tid":1676492,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b57urgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb57urgO.jpg&h=f79ce9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aWOxo3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaWOxo3x.jpg&h=7e665956&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54215219f58a5b7345b80a3a46968a12b5706a9a","tid":1676492,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGeTSYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGeTSYB.jpg&h=d60a8fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouDhAb